                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17670909-63-defend686 t17670909-63-punish374"></join>
               Death
            </rs>.</p>
               <p>Mills <rs id="t17670909-63-verdict375" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17670909-63-verdict375" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               guilty
            </rs>. <rs id="t17670909-63-punish376" type="punishmentDescription">
